<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/anna-turley> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Anna Turley was appointed Minister of State in the Cabinet Office (Minister without Portfolio) on 6 September 2025. She was previously Junior Lord of the Treasury (Government Whip) from 10 July 2024 to 6 September 2025. She was elected as the MP for Redcar in July 2024."@en .
